  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Event Graphic Designer",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Duties</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Gather information and materials needed for each project.</li>\n  <li>Plan and develop concepts based on client needs and project requirements.</li>\n  <li>Create rough layouts of artwork, copy, and overall design direction.</li>\n  <li>Share drafts for feedback and make adjustments as needed.</li>\n  <li>Prepare final artwork for print or digital use, coordinating with vendors when necessary.</li>\n  <li>Work closely with clients, providing advice on design style, format, production, and timelines.</li>\n  <li>Design graphics, layouts, event logos, and mockups.</li>\n  <li>Coordinate with external partners like agencies, printers, or art services.</li>\n  <li>Support team projects and help out where needed.</li>\n  <li>Knowledge in 3D rendering and video editing.</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>Key Skills</h3>\n<ul>\n  <li>Strong skills in design and video editing software.</li>\n  <li>Creative and able to come up with fresh ideas.</li>\n  <li>Good at managing time and staying organized.</li>\n  <li>Detail-oriented and accurate in work.</li>\n  <li>Up to date with design trends and able to apply them.</li>\n  <li>Professional in handling deadlines, and project requirements.</li>\n</ul>",
