    "description": "<p>Not just another run of the mill event company in Singapore, SE7EN FRIDAY is made up of various specialists from different facets of production houses, coming together to synergize our expertise and leverage on each event team member's talents. Many of our team members are top, well-known, #1 within the events company Singapore industry, complementing our event industry partners.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>PASSION is the underlying sense you get from us from the moment we start corresponding and putting your perfect event together.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>The very reason why we call our company SE7EN FRIDAY Event Company in Singapore is because we treat every day as a Happy Friday! Our sense of purpose in this industry is clear and we know how to achieve this for our customers.</p>",
